{"tid":1154361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港電台仆街死] 務請各位　提　防　FAKE　NEWS！","createTime":"2019-05-14T08:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T14:36:07.000Z","uid":206224,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18654abcde35a9fb0a79f577ecd471ffce628dd5","tid":1154361,"uid":206224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T08:51:09.000Z","msg":"而家逃犯條例絕對係一場香港人面對嘅空前大危機<br />\n咁難得呢次泛民咁生性，希望大家係睇新聞嘅時候，多d探究多同埋批判性思考，唔好媒體講咩就信咩，因為而家好多媒體都非常不持平，用FAKE NEWS製造分化<br />\n<br />\n例如今日香港電台有個新聞如下:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457443-20190514.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457443-20190514.htm&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZ%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=4f83c99a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1457443-20190514.htm&h=83a3e505\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1457443-20190514.htm</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>建制派歡迎三方協商<span style=\"color: red;\"> 民主派：撤回修訂非前設</span><br />\n對於民主黨議員涂謹申提出，由政府、建制派和民主派議員三方協商，處理修訂《逃犯條例》的困局。建制派表示歡迎，但認為各方必須派出有能力決定的代表出席，否則浪費時間。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民主派表示願意參與對話，又指撤回修例，並非對話前設</span>。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n睇落係咪好似覺得泛民縮沙賣港？<br />\n但如果你有禁入條LINK去聽個錄音，你會發現呢段新聞文字描述根本就係斷章取義<br />\n實質上，毛孟靜係錄音到純粹係講呢條惡法好撚ON9，錄音中佢嘅原句如下：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&ldquo;<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">林鄭係講得好清楚: 「<span style=\"color: green;\">你純粹要求我撤回條條例嘅話呢，就唔洗傾啦～</span>」咁我暫時唔同你講撤回先！咁你有咩野其他嘅空間？可以不撤回，（而係）擱置，係嗎？</span></strong>&rdquo;</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港電台，仆街死啦！</span>"},{"pid":"01e5a738841485b39fd81ab069acf2b1dcee4251","tid":1154361,"uid":149041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476547692332a0b97489f17b4eec9e2b9c31cd34","tid":1154361,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"港台搞乜"},{"pid":"fa716429220aa2ee521f3cce69227ffd2396c1d4","tid":1154361,"uid":35305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"476547692332a0b97489f17b4eec9e2b9c31cd34","tid":1154361,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T09:44:39.000Z","msg":"港台搞乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"港台唔係一向比較中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b26699c6089c71b53cc27420e7280d6270644d","tid":1154361,"uid":79382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:56:03.000Z","msg":"睇完字、聽完錄音，都唔知有咩問題<br />\n不如樓主你講下呢段文字有咩誤導啲地方？"},{"pid":"82f851b7c6f26d5bf67b6de8425c6f89c6b4b660","tid":1154361,"uid":79382,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T14:00:40.000Z","msg":"同埋樓主你都quote少咗句<br />\n毛孟靜仲接住講：「停一停，睇下有咩空間喺入面可以傾落去」<br />\n連埋晒一齊，用佢段稿嗰一句嚟總結，有咩錯？"},{"pid":"fdfcce65aefd3b22fdd3980d89a05d31b7d93142","tid":1154361,"uid":184279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"負評係俾樓豬"}]}